 usage of its website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span class="accent">Studioplugins.net</span> also collects potentially personally-identifying information like Internet Protocol (IP) addresses for logged in users and for users leaving comments on https://Studioplugins.net blog posts. <span class="accent">Studioplugins.net</span> only discloses logged in user and commenter IP addresses under the same circumstances that it uses and discloses personally-identifying information as described below.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Gathering of Personally-Identifying Information</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Certain visitors to <span class="accent">Studioplugins.net\'s</span> websites choose to interact with <span class="accent">Studioplugins.net</span> in ways that require <span class="accent">Studioplugins.net</span> to gather personally-identifying information. The amount and type of information that Studioplugins.net gathers depends on the nature of the interaction. For example, we ask visitors who sign up for a blog at https://Studioplugins.net to provide a username and email address.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Security</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The security of your Personal Information is important to us, but remember that no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your Personal Information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Advertisements</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ads appearing on our website may be delivered to users by advertising partners, who may set cookies. These cookies allow the ad server to recognize your computer each time they send you an online advertisement to compile information about you or others who use your computer. This information allows ad networks to, among other things, deliver targeted advertisements that they believe will be of most interest to you. This Privacy Policy covers the use of cookies by <span class="accent">Studioplugins.net</span> and does not cover the use of cookies by any advertisers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Links To External Sites</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our Service may contain links to external sites that are not operated by us. If you click on a third party link, you will be directed to that third party\'s site. We strongly advise you to review the Privacy Policy and terms and conditions of every site you visit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We have no control over, and assume no responsibility for the content, privacy policies or practices of any third party sites, products or services.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '<span class="title">Privacy <span class=\'accent\'>policy</span></span>', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-06-18 13:19:11', '2020-06-18 10:19:11', '', 3, 'http://artuplugins.loc/2020/06/18/3-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
	(101, 1, '2020-06-18 13:24:15', '2020-06-18 10:24:15', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Studioplugins.net may collect statistics about the behavior of visitors to its website. Studioplugins.net may display this information publicly or provide it to others. However, Studioplugins.net does not disclose your personally-identifying information.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Cookies</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To enrich and perfect your online experience, Studioplugins.net uses "Cookies", similar technologies and services provided by others to display personalized content, appropriate advertising and store your preferences on your computer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A cookie is a string of information that a website stores on a visitor\'s computer, and that the visitor\'s browser provides to the website each time the visitor returns. Studioplugins.net uses cookies to help Studioplugins.net identify and track visitors, their usage of https://Studioplugins.net, and their website access preferences. Studioplugins.net visitors who do not wish to have cookies placed on their computers should set their browsers to refuse cookies before using Pixleaks.com\'s websites, with the drawback that certain features of Studioplugins.net\'s websites may not function properly without the aid of cookies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By continuing to navigate our website without changing your cookie settings, you hereby acknowledge and agree to Studioplugins.net\'s use of cookies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Privacy Policy Changes</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Although most changes are likely to be minor, Studioplugins.net may change its Privacy Policy from time to time, and in Studioplugins.net\'s sole discretion. Studioplugins.net encourages visitors to frequently check this page for any changes to its Privacy Policy. Your contin